Invocation Name: snoqualmie pass status
des: Ever wish you could ask Alexa for the current status of I-90 Snoqualmie Pass? Now you can! Using WSDOT's API, Snoqualmie Pass Status provides the latest status and pictures of the Snoqualmie Pass. Perfect for checking conditions before going skiing or heading over the pass!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
